trans-unit.source: Provides a strongly typed collection of <xref href="System.Diagnostics.CounterCreationData"></xref> objects.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.CounterCreationDataCollection"></xref> class, with no associated <xref href="System.Diagnostics.CounterCreationData"></xref> instances.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.CounterCreationDataCollection"></xref> class by using the specified array of <xref href="System.Diagnostics.CounterCreationData"></xref> instances.
